Package com.ogprover.prover_protocol.cp.geoconstruction

Interface Summary
ConicSection Interface description: Interface for general conic section
SetOfPoints Interface description: Interface for all sets of points like lines, circles and ellipses
SpecialConstantAngle Interface description: Interface for special constant angles (like 30 degrees, or 60, 45, 90, 18, 36, 72 and others that can be constructed)
